ure favorable outcomes."}]]}]]}]]}]}]
15:["$","article","Competition",{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/[0.04] to-white/[0.02] overflow-hidden","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-5 md:[&>*:first-child]:order-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"relative md:col-span-2 h-56 md:h-full min-h-56","children":[["$","$L10",null,{"src":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?w=1200&h=700&fit=crop","alt":"Competition legal services","fill":true,"className":"object-cover"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t md:bg-gradient-to-r from-black/50 to-transparent"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"md:col-span-3 p-6 md:p-8","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/20 text-sm text-slate-200","children":4}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold","style":{"color":"#F8E48B"},"children":"Competition"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3","children":[["$","p","As the UAE continues opening to global markets, compliance with competition law is essential. We advise on UAE Competition Law (Federal Law No. 4 of 2012), merger control regulations, and anti-competitive risk.",{"className":"text-slate-200 leading-relaxed","children":"As the UAE continues opening to global markets, compliance with competition law is essential. We advise on UAE Competition Law (Federal Law No. 4 of 2012), merger control regulations, and anti-competitive risk."}],["$","p","Our services include agreement reviews, merger clearance support, defense in cartel and dominance investigations, and pricing policy guidance to reduce regulatory exposure while preserving market strength.",{"className":"text-slate-200 leading-relaxed","children":"Our services include agreement reviews, merger clearance support, defense in cartel and dominance investigations, and pricing 